tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE political_party_memberships (
  membership_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  party_name VARCHAR(255),
  member_name VARCHAR(255),
  membership_start_date DATE,
  membership_end_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE member (
    member_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    member_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    member_birthdate DATE,
    member_gender CHAR(1),
    party_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (party_id) REFERENCES party(party_id)
);

CREATE TABLE member_affiliation (
    member_id INT,
    affiliation_id INT,
    PRIMARY KEY (member_id, affiliation_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (member_id) REFERENCES member(member_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (affiliation_id) REFERENCES affiliation(affiliation_id)
);

CREATE TABLE political_parties (
    party_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    party_name TEXT,
    party_ideology TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE party_members (
    member_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    member_name TEXT,
    party_id INT,
    membership_status TEXT,
    join_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE party_affiliations (
    affiliation_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    affiliation_name TEXT,
    affiliated_party_id INT
)

CREATE TABLE membership_fees (
    fee_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    fee_amount DECIMAL,
    fee_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE membership_history (
    history_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    member_id INT,
    affiliation_id INT,
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE
)
